      <title>个人博客新手Mac搭建实操</title>
      <link href="/2022/03/19/hexo-stun%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98/"/>
      <url>/2022/03/19/hexo-stun%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="准备GitHub账号并新建一个博客仓库（Gitee搭建点击这里）">          <a href="#准备GitHub账号并新建一个博客仓库（Gitee搭建点击这里）" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#准备GitHub账号并新建一个博客仓库（Gitee搭建点击这里）" class="headerlink" title="准备GitHub账号并新建一个博客仓库（Gitee搭建点击这里）"></a>准备<span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link" href="https://github.com/">GitHub账号</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span>并新建一个博客仓库（Gitee搭建<span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link" href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_46036214/article/details/110137239">点击这里</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span>）</h3>      <p>仓库命名必须为<strong>username.github.io</strong>且为<strong>公开状态</strong><br>eg.<br>        <img class="lazyload lazyload-gif" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="/posts_photos/0.png" alt="示例图片">      </p>        <h3 id="准备工具">          <a href="#准备工具" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#准备工具" class="headerlink" title="准备工具"></a>准备工具</h3>              <h4 id="homebrew安装vscode">          <a href="#homebrew安装vscode" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#homebrew安装vscode" class="headerlink" title="homebrew安装vscode"></a>homebrew安装vscode</h4>      <pre class="line-numbers language-zsh" data-language="zsh"><code class="language-zsh">homebrew install --cask visual-studio-code<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>        <h3 id="部署hexo框架">          <a href="#部署hexo框架" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#部署hexo框架" class="headerlink" title="部署hexo框架"></a>部署hexo框架</h3>              <h4 id="node-js安装">          <a href="#node-js安装" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#node-js安装" class="headerlink" title="node.js安装"></a>node.js安装</h4>      <pre class="line-numbers language-zsh" data-language="zsh"><code class="language-zsh">brew install node<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>        <h4 id="hexo框架安装">          <a href="#hexo框架安装" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#hexo框架安装" class="headerlink" title="hexo框架安装"></a>hexo框架安装</h4>      <pre class="line-numbers language-zsh" data-language="zsh"><code class="language-zsh">npm install -g hexo-cli <span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>        <h4 id="新建博客文件夹并初始化hexo">          <a href="#新建博客文件夹并初始化hexo" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#新建博客文件夹并初始化hexo" class="headerlink" title="新建博客文件夹并初始化hexo"></a>新建博客文件夹并初始化hexo</h4>      <pre class="line-numbers language-zsh" data-language="zsh"><code class="language-zsh">mkdir blog &amp;&amp; hexo init<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>        <h4 id="修改hexo目录下配置文件">          <a href="#修改hexo目录下配置文件" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#修改hexo目录下配置文件" class="headerlink" title="修改hexo目录下配置文件"></a>修改hexo目录下配置文件</h4>      <pre class="line-numbers language-zsh" data-language="zsh"><code class="language-zsh">vi _config.yml<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>将示例图中<strong>repository</strong>修改为你的GitHub博客仓库即可。<br>        <img class="lazyload lazyload-gif" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="/posts_photos/1.png" alt="示例图片">      </p>        <h4 id="安装hexo推送插件并推送至GitHub">          <a href="#安装hexo推送插件并推送至GitHub" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#安装hexo推送插件并推送至GitHub" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo推送插件并推送至GitHub"></a>安装hexo推送插件并推送至GitHub</h4>      <pre class="line-numbers language-zsh" data-language="zsh"><code class="language-zsh">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save &amp;&amp; hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><strong>至此hexo博客搭建完成，访问username.github.io即可</strong>（username为你的GitHub用户名）</p>        <h3 id="stun主题安装">          <a href="#stun主题安装" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#stun主题安装" class="headerlink" title="stun主题安装"></a>stun主题安装</h3>      <pre class="line-numbers language-zsh" data-language="zsh"><code class="language-zsh">git clone https://github.com/liuyib/hexo-theme-stun.git themes/stun<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>        <h3 id="修改网站标题等信息">          <a href="#修改网站标题等信息" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#修改网站标题等信息" class="headerlink" title="修改网站标题等信息"></a>修改网站标题等信息</h3>              <h4 id="终端进入博客文件夹执行命令使用vscode打开项目">          <a href="#终端进入博客文件夹执行命令使用vscode打开项目" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#终端进入博客文件夹执行命令使用vscode打开项目" class="headerlink" title="终端进入博客文件夹执行命令使用vscode打开项目"></a>终端进入博客文件夹执行命令使用vscode打开项目</h4>      <pre class="line-numbers language-zsh" data-language="zsh"><code class="language-zsh">code ./ <span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>        <h4 id="修改bolg目录下的-config-yml文件">          <a href="#修改bolg目录下的-config-yml文件" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#修改bolg目录下的-config-yml文件" class="headerlink" title="修改bolg目录下的_config.yml文件"></a>修改bolg目录下的_config.yml文件</h4>      <p><strong>title</strong>、<strong>subtitle</strong>、<strong>author</strong>、<strong>language</strong>、<strong>url</strong><br>        <img class="lazyload lazyload-gif" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="/posts_photos/2.png" alt="示例图片">      <br><strong>theme</strong>修改为<strong>stun</strong><br>        <img class="lazyload lazyload-gif" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="/posts_photos/7.png" alt="示例图片">      <br><strong>每次修改bolg配置文件后可在mac终端中bolg目录下执行hexo s本地部署，访问<span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link" href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span> 查看修改效果</strong>，下同</p>        <h3 id="自用stun主题配置">          <a href="#自用stun主题配置" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#自用stun主题配置" class="headerlink" title="自用stun主题配置"></a>自用stun主题配置</h3>              <h4 id="终端执行新增首页分类、标签按钮命令">          <a href="#终端执行新增首页分类、标签按钮命令" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#终端执行新增首页分类、标签按钮命令" class="headerlink" title="终端执行新增首页分类、标签按钮命令"></a>终端执行新增首页分类、标签按钮命令</h4>      <pre class="line-numbers language-zsh" data-language="zsh"><code class="language-zsh">hexo new page tags &amp;&amp; hexo new page categories<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><strong>vscode</strong>编辑<strong>source</strong>目录下对应文件夹中的<strong>index.md</strong>，加上<strong>type</strong>字段，如：<br>        <img class="lazyload lazyload-gif" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="/posts_photos/3.png" alt="示例图片">      <br>去除<strong>blog/themes/stun/<strong>下的</strong>_config.yml</strong>注释。<br>        <img class="lazyload lazyload-gif" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="/posts_photos/5.png" alt="示例图片">      </p>        <h4 id="更改博客首页图片信息">          <a href="#更改博客首页图片信息" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#更改博客首页图片信息" class="headerlink" title="更改博客首页图片信息"></a>更改博客首页图片信息</h4>      <p>首先在vscode中为<strong>blog/source/<strong>下新增一个图片存放目录</strong>stun_images</strong>并将需要使用的图片拖到改目录下；修改<strong>blog/themes/stun/<strong>下的</strong>_config.yml</strong>文件，ctrl+f搜索<strong>bg_image</strong>并设置为<strong>true</strong>，url中填写图片位置即可。<br>        <img class="lazyload lazyload-gif" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="/posts_photos/4.png" alt="示例图片">      </p>        <h4 id="修改个人头像">          <a href="#修改个人头像" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#修改个人头像" class="headerlink" title="修改个人头像"></a>修改个人头像</h4>      <p>上述**_config.yml<strong>文件，ctrl+f搜索</strong>author<strong>并设置为</strong>true<strong>，url中填写图片位置即可，</strong>motto**自行修改为想要的内容。<br>        <img class="lazyload lazyload-gif" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="/posts_photos/6.png" alt="示例图片">      </p>        <h4 id="添加网站主体特效">          <a href="#添加网站主体特效" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#添加网站主体特效" class="headerlink" title="添加网站主体特效"></a>添加网站主体特效</h4>      <p>上述**_config.yml<strong>文件，ctrl+f搜索</strong>canvas_ribbon<strong>和</strong>canvas_nest<strong>依旧个人喜好设置为</strong>true**开启并设置特效幅度参数即可。</p>        <h4 id="添加右下角2d玩偶">          <a href="#添加右下角2d玩偶" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#添加右下角2d玩偶" class="headerlink" title="添加右下角2d玩偶"></a>添加右下角2d玩偶</h4>      <pre class="line-numbers language-zsh" data-language="zsh"><code class="language-zsh">npm install --save live2d-widget-model-hijiki &amp;&amp; npm install --save live2d-widget-model-hijiki <span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>在blog/修改yml文件，新增如下内容：<br>live2d:<br>  enable: true  # 是否启动<br>  scriptFrom: local # 默认<br>  pluginRootPath: live2dw/  # 插件在站点上的根目录(相对路径)<br>  pluginJsPath: lib/  # 脚本文件相对与插件根目录路径<br>  pluginModelPath: assets/  # 模型文件相对与插件根目录路径<br>  tagMode: false  # 标签模式, 是否仅替换 live2d tag标签而非插入到所有页面中<br>  debug: false  # 调试, 是否在控制台输出日志<br>  model:<br>    use: live2d-widget-model-hijiki  ## 模型文件<br>  display:<br>    position: right # 定位方向 left right top bottom<br>    width: 150  # 小人宽度<br>    height: 300 #  小人高度<br>    hOffset: -15  # 向 偏移<br>    vOffset: -15  # 像 偏移<br>  mobile:<br>    show: true  # 手机端是否显示<br>  react:<br>    opacity: 1.0  # 模型透明度</p><p><strong>至此博客的基本美化配置已完成，保存修改后终端执行hexo s查看部署效果，执行hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d 部署至GitHub后可以通过username.github.io进行访问</strong></p>        <h3 id="拓展1-Gitalk评论系统">          <a href="#拓展1-Gitalk评论系统" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#拓展1-Gitalk评论系统" class="headerlink" title="拓展1:Gitalk评论系统"></a>拓展1:Gitalk评论系统</h3>      <p>首先需要<span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link" href="https://github.com/settings/applications/new">注册GitHubApplication授权</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span>获取<strong>client_id</strong>和<strong>client_secret</strong><br>修改<strong>blog/themes/stun/_config.yml</strong>文件即可。<br>        <img class="lazyload lazyload-gif" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="/posts_photos/8.png" alt="示例图片">      </p><blockquote><p><span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link" href="https://theme-stun.github.io/docs/zh-CN/advanced/advanced.html#%E5%B9%B3%E6%BB%91%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7">其余stun拓展</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span><br><span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link" href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV11a41127pt?spm_id_from=333.880.my_history.page.click">美化视频参照</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span></p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
